commit.message: Replace deprecated given/when with if/elsif/else
Add changes to v10. I should have filled this before the release...
dzil: prepend the tag name with v

Fix new version number in the copied Makefile.PL

I need to do something to avoid this failure mode during release
Bump version
update version to 10
Add Gtk3-ImageView-* to gitignore
Make tests more happy

Fix set('resolution-ratio')

$pspec->get_name converts hyphens to underscores

See https://metacpan.org/pod/Glib::Object::Subclass

Rewrite Selector tool: it now supports dragging and doesn't block doubleclick

This functionality existed in Gtk2::ImageView

Add the generated Makefile.PL

Due to https://github.com/carygravel/gtk3-imageview/pull/26#issuecomment-843086078

Delete the manifest test, because manifest is autogenerated now anyway,
and not in git, which makes the copied-to-git Makefile.PL to fail the
manifest test when running without dzil

Use Dist::Zilla

One benefit is that it can automatically change the version number in
all the .pm files
Another is that it can automatically gather dependencies

The breaking change is that "make tidy" is now "dzil perltidy"
